001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.parameters;
002
003/**
004 * Defines a data interception contract for UI-driven API interactions.
005 *
006 * <p>Implementations specify which endpoint responses to intercept by providing
007 * a substring match, along with an enum constant to identify the intercept flow.
008 *
009 * @param <T> the enum type used to identify specific intercept implementations
010 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate ğŸ’ğŸ‘¨ğŸ’»
011 */
012public interface DataIntercept<T extends Enum<T>> {
013
014   /**
015    * Returns the substring used to match the target endpoint for interception.
016    *
017    * <p>This substring is used to filter API calls whose URL contains it.
018    *
019    * @return the endpoint substring to intercept
020    */
021   String getEndpointSubString();
022
023   /**
024    * Returns the enum constant identifying this data intercept implementation.
025    *
026    * <p>The returned enum value is used to look up the corresponding interception logic.
027    *
028    * @return the enum representing this intercept
029    */
030   T enumImpl();
031
032}
